comments: VanVleet (TOR) briefly places two hands on Walker (BOS) during his dribble but VanVleet immediately removes both hands.
Anunoby (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Tatum (BOS) during the drive.

Tatum (BOS) slightly extends his leg during the release of his jump shot attempt and it makes marginal contact to Anunoby's (TOR) leg as he jumps forward to contest the shot. Anunoby is able to land safely following the contact.
Siakam (TOR) and Williams (BOS) engage in incidental foot to foot contact off ball that sends Siakam to the floor. He then engages in incidental foot to foot contact with Brown (BOS).
Lowry (TOR) and Smart (BOS) make incidental contact with one another while attempting to gather the loose ball.
Prior to the illegal contact that results in a called shooting foul, Lowry (TOR) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes more than two steps during his driving shot attempt.
Theis (BOS) makes contact to Lowry's (TOR) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) reaches across and makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) at the start of his drive.
Powell (TOR) swipes down and avoids making contact to Tatum (BOS) during his driving shot attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) makes marginal contact to Tatum's (BOS) body after the release of the ball during his driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (TOR) clamps Williams' (BOS) arm during the rebound.
Smart (BOS) successfully blocks Powell's (TOR) shot attempt. While reaching for the ball in a natural motion, he brushes and makes incidental head contact as a result.
Siakam (TOR) jumps vertically and absorbs the oncoming body contact from Walker (BOS) as he jumps to pass at the end of the drive.
Ibaka (TOR) makes marginal contact with Smart (BOS) while boxing him out on the free throw attempt.
Siakam (TOR) briefly grasps Williams' (BOS) shorts during the rebound but he immediately releases them.
Powell (TOR) makes contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm while he is airborne during the rebound and the contact affects his FOM.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact to Williams' (BOS) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Smart (BOS) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Williams (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Anunoby (TOR) commits a take foul on Walker (BOS) in the backcourt.
Powell (TOR) is firming up when he and Tatum (BOS) make marginal contact with one another during the screen.
Following foot to foot contact with his teammate, Tatum (BOS) falls to the floor and avoids making contact to Siakam (TOR) during his jump shot attempt.
